messages.subject: Going no mail
messages.msgSnippet: I have some writing and other deadlines - some self imposed yet all very important to me - coming up and I have a tendency to use my meagre alone time reading
messages.messageBody:
I have some writing and other deadlines - some self imposed yet all very important to me - coming up and I have a tendency to use my meagre alone time reading email. Anything to procrastinate actual writing/crafting work!

Therefore I am going No Mail very temporarily. See you all soon, with good news about writing successes I hope.

If anyone needs to speak to me specifically please go ahead off list. I will still be checking my mail often, just reducing volume for the time being.

Robyn L. Coburn
www.Iggyjingles.etsy.com
www.iggyjingles.blogspot.com

[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
